  <h1>WiFi Priority ‚Äì Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 09/13/2025<br>
     <strong>Last Updated:</strong> 09/13/2025</p>

  <p>WiFi Priority (‚Äúwe,‚Äù ‚Äúus,‚Äù or ‚Äúour‚Äù) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how the app handles your data and permissions.</p>

  <h2>1. Information You Provide Directly</h2>
  <p>When using WiFi Priority, you may enter:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Wi-Fi network names (SSIDs)</li>
    <li>Wi-Fi credentials (if required by your device)</li>
    <li>Your preferred priority order for networks</li>
  </ul>
  <p>This information is used solely to facilitate local app functionality and is not collected, transmitted, or stored remotely.</p>

  <h2>2. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
  <p>WiFi Priority does not collect or store any of the following:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Personally identifiable information (PII)</li>
    <li>Network credentials or configurations outside your device</li>
    <li>Your physical location or usage behavior</li>
  </ul>
  <p>No data leaves your device.</p>

  <h2>3. Crash Reporting & Diagnostics</h2>
  <p>We use Firebase Crashlytics to help us diagnose and fix technical issues. This service may automatically collect:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Device type and OS version</li>
    <li>App version</li>
    <li>Crash logs and technical diagnostics</li>
  </ul>
  <p>Crashlytics data is anonymized and used solely to improve app stability.</p>

  <h2>4. Permissions We Require</h2>
  <p>To deliver expected functionality, WiFi Priority may request access to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Wi-Fi status and connection state</li>
    <li>Ability to view available networks</li>
    <li>Modify Wi-Fi connections</li>
  </ul>
  <p>These permissions are required to enable prioritization of networks on your device only.</p>

  <h2>5. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <p>Your data is used to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Automatically connect to preferred Wi-Fi networks based on your priority settings</li>
    <li>Notify you when switching between networks</li>
    <li>Help improve app performance and stability</li>
    <li>Provide customer support if you reach out for help</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Data Storage and Security</h2>
  <p>All data remains on your device. We take reasonable steps to ensure that data processed within the app is handled securely and never shared with third parties.</p>

  <h2>7. Children‚Äôs Privacy</h2>
  <p>WiFi Priority is not intended for users under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.</p>

  <h2>8. Policy Updates</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any material changes will be communicated through the app or our website. Continued use of the app indicates your agreement to the latest policy.</p>

  <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
